334
00:32:27,400 --> 00:32:30,612
Um, dois, três, quatro.

335
00:32:30,613 --> 00:32:33,111
Um, dois...

336
00:32:38,053 --> 00:32:39,973
BAILE DE INVERNO

337
00:32:41,987 --> 00:32:44,669
Eu sempre quis dançar
com o Chiqueirinho.

338
00:32:48,845 --> 00:32:53,032
